Stuart, thanks for the review and the nice question aroused. 

It does indeed affect v2 api as well: 

glance --os-image-api-version 2 image-list

causes HTTPInternalServerError (HTTP 500).

I'd prefer to fix the bug in v2 in a separate patch if no one has any objections.

This looks good. I'm curious Inessa why you want to fix v2 separately, but that isn't a blocker to merging this in my opinion.
